### Session Checklist (every session)
```
ALWAYS:
  1. Paste intsructions.txt as first message
  2. Attach Phase1A_Adjustments_and_Fixes.md
  3. Attach the relevant Plans/Text/*.txt for that day's section
  4. Select the appropriate speckit agent from the dropdown

IMPLEMENT SESSIONS ONLY:
  5. Attach java-springboot/SKILL.md

YOUR ARGUMENT TO THE AGENT:
